Class PlayerControllerCommand

java.lang.Object
  ch.ethz.dcg.jukefox.playmode.PlayerControllerCommand

public class PlayerControllerCommand
extends java.lang.Object

An object of this class represents a command that can be executed on a Playlist. Use the static methods to create a command of s specific type
